reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Simple and what we needed
reviews.reviewText: Looks really nice. Definitely smaller than expected, since I'm not good at seeing the size image and knowing what that will look like in my room ;) But purchased to hold grandbaby items in our home and will be perfect for that. Inexpensive and will meet our simple needs. For the price, impressed with the quality!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for small rooms
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for small rooms and the draws hold a lot. Easy to assemble and looks very clean and nice accent to the room. Great price and product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: Super easy to assemble and very sturdy. It’s a bit shorter than I expected but I’m fine with that. It fits perfectly into the space I wanted it in! One of the parts did come a little bent but I hammered it into shape before assembling that part.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to build
reviews.reviewText: Kind of short but it’s compact for small spaces! Loved the outcome and how easy it was to set up. Will be using to store my baby’s clothes 🥰

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I am not using this for clothes. I am using this to store lids from my pots & pans.So far so good.I can't get on the floor to put these together. Not w/o having to call EMTs. So sitting on the couch made putting it together a little harder. There are no instructions on how to do things. It's like putting together a puzzle :-}Very nice looking and sturdy. I suggest this for someone no matter the need. Just think outside the box.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Buyer Beware, has some issues
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Overall the product isn't bad. Easy to assemble, looks pretty good, stable, and doesn't have a smell that some of these products do. I was able to get it together in 30 minutes but did have three issues.First, one of the drawer supports was bent and I had to bend it back to get the middle section connected.Second, one of the drawers has extremely crooked holes for the handles and looks pretty not great.Third, the two drawers in the center are wedged in so tight that you can't pull them out. I'm hoping if I loosen the sides a little bit it'll give it enough space to slide out, but I'm concerned it's going to compromise stability.They did include a card if you have issues so I will be contacting them, but overall mediocre product. If it wasn't such a pain to send back I probably would but it's going in a closet anyway where no one will see it.
